snippet.title: ASTRONEER - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore and exploit distant worlds in ASTRONEER: A game of aerospace industry and interplanetary exploration.

Coming to Steam Early Access: http://store.steampowered.com/app/361420/
